						<div class="customHelpBody">
							The Risk &amp; Market Assessment informs the Go/No Go decision and must be completed in its entirety prior to submitting the go/no go recommendation for approval.  If you do not know the answer to a question, select ‘unknown’.
							<div style="width:100%; height:5px;"></div>
								<strong>Directions:</strong>
								<ul>
									<li>Step 1:  Create a version name for the Risk &amp; Market Assessment (default will be saved as “Initial Assessment”)</li>
									<li>Step 2:  Complete the Risk Assessment</li>
									<li>Step 3:  Complete the Market Assessment</li>
									<li>Step 4: Schedule and conduct a Go/No Go meeting (optional)</li>
									<li>Step 5:  Select “go” or “no go” for approval</li>
									<li>Step 6:  Submit the completed R&amp;M Assessment and go/no go recommendation for approval </li>
								</ul>
								<em>The system will automatically submit the request to the owning organization P&amp;L Manger or delegate.  The approver will review the results of the Risk &amp; Market Assessment and approve/reject the go/no go recommendation.</em>
						</div>
					</div>	
				</div>
		 
				<apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="questionnaire" id="theAccordion" >
					<apex:pageBlock title="{!Questionnaire__c.Name} Risk Assessment Details" id="theBlock" >
						<apex:pageBlockButtons location="both"> 
							<apex:commandButton action="{!SavePrevious}" value="Save & Previous" rerender="pageMessages" onClick="showModal();" onComplete="hideModal();" disabled="{!oQuestionnaire.QuestionnaireSet__r.ApprovalStatus__c=='Approved'}" />
							<apex:commandButton action="{!SaveNext}" value="Save & Next" rerender="pageMessages" onClick="showModal();" onComplete="hideModal();"  disabled="{!oQuestionnaire.QuestionnaireSet__r.ApprovalStatus__c=='Approved'}"/>
							
							<apex:commandButton action="{!SaveRecord}" value="Save" rerender="pageMessages, countBlock" onClick="showModal();" onComplete="hideModal();"  disabled="{!oQuestionnaire.QuestionnaireSet__r.ApprovalStatus__c=='Approved'}"/>
							<apex:commandButton action="{!ReturnToSummary}" value="Return to Summary" rerender="pageMessages" onClick="showModal();" onComplete="hideModal();" />
						</apex:pageBlockButtons>

						<apex:pageBlockSection collapsible="false" title="Risk Assessment"></apex:pageBlockSection>
